headline: EOG Resources Inc. (EOG) is a ‘Buy’ on Encino Integration and Expansion Plans: UBS
summary: EOG Resources Inc. (NYSE:EOG) is one of the most profitable energy stocks to buy right now. On October 9, analysts at UBS reiterated a ‘Buy’ rating on the stock with a $144 price target following a tour of the company’s facilities in Ohio.
